---
interface Props {
  title: string;
  body: string;
  href: string;
}

const { href, title, body } = Astro.props;
---

<div class="faq-component">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl divide-y divide-gray-900/10 px-6 py-32 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold leading-10 tracking-tight text-blue-500 text-center mb-8">
      Frequently Asked Questions
    </h2>
    <dl class="space-y-6 divide-y divide-gray-900/10">
      <div class="pt-6">
        <dt>
          <button type="button" class="flex w-full items-start justify-between text-left text-gray-900" aria-controls="faq-0" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="text-base font-semibold leading-7">How can I get started on my project with FLY Studios LK?</span>
            <span class="ml-6 flex h-7 items-center">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
              </svg>
            </span>
          </button>
        </dt>
        <dd class="mt-2 pr-12 hidden" id="faq-0">
          <p class="text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">To get started, simply contact us through our website, email, or phone. We'll schedule a consultation to discuss your project goals, budget, and timeline, and provide you with a plan for moving forward.</p>
        </dd>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-6">
        <dt>
          <button type="button" class="flex w-full items-start justify-between text-left text-gray-900" aria-controls="faq-1" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="text-base font-semibold leading-7">Can I hire FLY Studios LK for international projects?</span>
            <span class="ml-6 flex h-7 items-center">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
              </svg>
            </span>
          </button>
        </dt>
        <dd class="mt-2 pr-12 hidden" id="faq-1">
          <p class="text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Yes, we are open to working on international projects! Please reach out to us with the details, and we'll discuss how we can best serve your needs.</p>
        </dd>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-6">
        <dt>
          <button type="button" class="flex w-full items-start justify-between text-left text-gray-900" aria-controls="faq-2" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="text-base font-semibold leading-7">How long does it take to complete a project?</span>
            <span class="ml-6 flex h-7 items-center">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
              </svg>
            </span>
          </button>
        </dt>
        <dd class="mt-2 pr-12 hidden" id="faq-2">
          <p class="text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">The timeline for completing a project varies depending on its scope and complexity. After discussing the project details with you, we will provide an estimated timeline.</p>
        </dd>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-6">
        <dt>
          <button type="button" class="flex w-full items-start justify-between text-left text-gray-900" aria-controls="faq-3" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="text-base font-semibold leading-7">Can I hire FLY Studios LK for both small and large-scale productions?</span>
            <span class="ml-6 flex h-7 items-center">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
              </svg>
            </span>
          </button>
        </dt>
        <dd class="mt-2 pr-12 hidden" id="faq-3">
          <p class="text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Yes, we cater to all kinds of projects, from small-scale productions like social media content to large-scale film and TV productions. No matter the size, we approach every project with the same level of professionalism and creativity.</p>
        </dd>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-6">
        <dt>
          <button type="button" class="flex w-full items-start justify-between text-left text-gray-900" aria-controls="faq-4" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="text-base font-semibold leading-7">Can FLY Studios LK help with scriptwriting and creative direction?</span>
            <span class="ml-6 flex h-7 items-center">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
              </svg>
            </span>
          </button>
        </dt>
        <dd class="mt-2 pr-12 hidden" id="faq-4">
          <p class="text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Our creative team can assist with concept development, scriptwriting, and overall creative direction. We work closely with clients to bring their vision to life while providing professional insights to enhance the project.</p>
        </dd>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-6">
        <dt>
          <button type="button" class="flex w-full items-start justify-between text-left text-gray-900" aria-controls="faq-5" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="text-base font-semibold leading-7">Do you offer aerial (drone) videography?</span>
            <span class="ml-6 flex h-7 items-center">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
              </svg>
            </span>
          </button>
        </dt>
        <dd class="mt-2 pr-12 hidden" id="faq-5">
          <p class="text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Yes, we offer professional drone videography to capture stunning aerial shots for your project, whether it's a landscape, real estate, or a dynamic event setting.</p>
        </dd>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-6">
        <dt>
          <button type="button" class="flex w-full items-start justify-between text-left text-gray-900" aria-controls="faq-6" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="text-base font-semibold leading-7">How can I stay updated on my project's progress?</span>
            <span class="ml-6 flex h-7 items-center">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
              </svg>
            </span>
          </button>
        </dt>
        <dd class="mt-2 pr-12 hidden" id="faq-6">
          <p class="text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">We maintain regular communication with our clients throughout the project. You will be updated at key milestones, and we're always available to answer any questions you may have.</p>
        </dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
  function setupFAQ() {
    const faqItems = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-component dl > div');
    faqItems.forEach((item) => {
      const button = item.querySelector('button');
      const content = item.querySelector('dd');
      
      if (button && content) {
        button.addEventListener('click', () => {
          const expanded = button.getAttribute('aria-expanded') === 'true';
          button.setAttribute('aria-expanded', (!expanded).toString());
          content.classList.toggle('hidden');
          const svg = button.querySelector('svg');
          if (svg) {
            svg.style.transform = expanded ? 'rotate(0deg)' : 'rotate(180deg)';
          }
        });
      }
    });
  }

  // Run setupFAQ on initial load
  setupFAQ();

  // Re-run setupFAQ when the page content updates
  document.addEventListener('astro:after-swap', setupFAQ);
</script>

<style>
  button svg {
    transition: transform 0.2s ease-in-out;
  }
</style>